      Path: event:/Charles/Charles Hej
    firstQuestion:
      question: "Aren\u2019t you the coolest dish in the building! "
      answer: "Merci boque, you don\u2019t look half bad yourself mon petit chou!
        I feel a bit uncomfortable though.. "
    q1FollowUpQuestion1:
      question: 'Is that so? '
      answer: "Oui, see i\u2019ve got sand in both my shoes! But you can\u2019t be
        the \u201Ccoolest dish in the building\u201D while pouring sand all over
        the place! "
    q1FollowUpQuestion2:
      question: 'Why do you have sand in your shoes? '
      answer: 'Well where does anyone get sand in New York andouille! The beach of
        course! J''aime walking on the beach late at night. Can you blame me for
        taking a lonely stroll before a lively party like this one? '
    secondQuestion:
      question: "You look confused. What\u2019s up? "
      answer: "Ah bon? Non, I just though I smelled the familiar odeur of a passed
        lover\u2026 Brought back memories\u2026 "
    q2FollowUpQuestion1:
      question: 'Good or bad memories? '
      answer: "Just\u2026 memories\u2026 We had great times, but we had very different
        lives\u2026 "
    q2FollowUpQuestion2:
      question: 'How so? '
      answer: "They were a bit too\u2026 bold? I think I like my partner to be a
        bit less brave and more\u2026 smart, if you know what I mean."
    thirdQuestion:
      question: 'I saw you peeping out the window looking worried. '
      answer: "Oh you saw that? Hoh hoh! I\u2019m not scared of heights if that\u2019s
        what you think! No\u2026 I\u2019m just thinking of my beautiful cat. She
        must be so lonely all alone in my apartment. Oh mon petit minou\u2026 "
    q3FollowUpQuestion1:
      question: 'Wouldn''t you rather be at home? '
      answer: 'And miss all the drama! Pour rien au monde! Have you heard the rumor,
        whoo! The best gossip is always around these rich geezers!  '
    q3FollowUpQuestion2:
      question: 'You really are on the beam! Care for a dance? '
      answer: 'My my, an enticing offer indeed! '
    "hejD\xE5Fras": 'Au revoir '
